snippet.title: Amber Heard Chat with a Lawyer: We Talk Amber's Baby and Depp vs. Heard Updates
snippet.description:
Amber Heard / Johnny Depp / Amber Heard Baby / Depp vs. Heard Trial /

In this short clip, we chat a bit about the Virginia trial and Amber Heard's new baby. This video is a teaser for my 2-hour interview with lawyer Andrea Burkhart coming up on my channel later this week.

For more videos on Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard and other celebrity controversies, subscribe to my channel.

Andrea's twitter: https://twitter.com/aburkhartlaw
